professions school or from a program providing education or training in an allied health profession or; (b) comes
from a family with an annual income below a level based on low-income thresholds according to family size, published
by the U.S. Bureau of the Census, adjusted annually for changes in the Consumer Price Index and adjusted by the Secretary
for use in all health professions programs, 42 CFR 57.1804(b)(2).

