(4) For each program for which the Board waived a cost/benefit analysis, reasons for the waiver and the results of match,
if tabulated.

(5) A description of each matching agreement the Board rejected and an explanation of why it was rejected.

(6) A listing of any violations of matching agreements that have been alleged or identified, and a discussion of any
